,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T12:01:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主係咪俾mk仔當狗撚完又心軟</blockquote><br />\n唔喺 喺比朋友當狗撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd1bfd7cd89f87efbd2f3780871c418a1e52ff45","tid":417163,"uid":53794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T12:01:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>樓主係咪俾mk仔當狗撚完又心軟</blockquote><br />\n唔喺 喺比朋友當狗撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n講嚟聽下"},{"pid":"1ea68ee4c6c691f5a3e20c81ea5d1929e6151a37","tid":417163,"uid":103510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T12:02:46.000Z","msg":"身邊有係咁 成日鄧佢唔抵"},{"pid":"bdcd21f334bcdd5707210f30e8d971c81cf75f46","tid":417163,"uid":103510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T12:02:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>身邊有人係咁 成日鄧佢唔抵</blockquote>"},{"pid":"e3778b8844684e66b5d26678fc8e6b896cef6d2f","tid":417163,"uid":5207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T12:08:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>樓主係咪俾mk仔當狗撚完又心軟</blockquote><br />\n唔喺 喺比朋友當狗撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n講嚟聽下</blockquote><br />\n每次同A嗌交 都喺自己衰心軟同佢say sorry<br />\n但成件事情上我班朋友都覺呀A好過份 <br />\n唔明白我點解比呀A鬧完嚟都仲可以同佢做朋友<br />\n日子耐咗 就不斷重覆咁比A撚 自己亦察覺到佢真喺會過份濫用我嘅心軟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">利申 同A都識咗十年以上</span>"},{"pid":"692335b78e9b3ab1010adab982befef27692d883","tid":417163,"uid":52477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T12:09:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>樓主係咪俾mk仔當狗撚完又心軟</blockquote><br />\n唔喺 喺比朋友當狗撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n講嚟聽下</blockquote><br />\n每次同A嗌交 都喺自己衰心軟同佢say sorry<br />\n但成件事情上我班朋友都覺呀A好過份 <br />\n唔明白我點解比呀A鬧完嚟都仲可以同佢做朋友<br />\n日子耐咗 就不斷重覆咁比A撚 自己亦察覺到佢真喺會過份濫用我嘅心軟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">利申 同A都識咗十年以上</span></blockquote><br />\n一日下把 一世下把<br />\n<br />\n除非你轉死性"},{"pid":"3e16eccef00bae9d3dea37f6f23aba931576096e","tid":417163,"uid":5207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T12:11:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>身邊有係咁 成日鄧佢唔抵</blockquote><br />\n我朋友都喺鄧我唔抵 點解仲會有人忍到佢啲咁閪嘅語氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"572da233da1f0e2b96c0347727d5f83c39e511ce","tid":417163,"uid":5207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T12:13:22.000Z","msg":"簡單啲講 如果嗌交喺場比賽<br />\n輸嘅一定喺我<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db4897795ae477ed25e72c6108551f3bad87f598","tid":417163,"uid":92456,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T12:17:10.000Z","msg":"完全明白<br />\n所以腦入面永遠都係理性同感性嘅戰爭<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc124dbe4e85ebe9754d3051209ddee0cbdf0a05","tid":417163,"uid":5207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T12:22:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>完全明白<br />\n所以腦入面永遠都係理性同感性嘅戰爭<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n但永遠都喺輸比感性<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}